You can use the GET endpoint [Get box information for application](/api-documentation/docs/api/service/common-transit-convention-traders/1.0/oas/page#tag/Notifications/operation/getBoxInformationForApplication) to get box information for your application if there is a Push-Pull-Notification Service (PPNS) box.
